title: 109: The Forgotten Favorites Episode: Must-Buy Food Finds! (Retro Picks)
itunes:title: The Forgotten Favorites Episode: Must-Buy Food Finds! (Retro Picks)
description: In this week’s episode, Lisa and the gang are rediscovering some classic foods: rice cakes, whipped yogurt, coffee creamer, Fiber One, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, Lisa shares some throwback recipes AND new HG creations that are perfect for right now! So come aboard our virtual DeLorean as we go back to the future…  And don’t forget to head on over to our Foodcast page for the products and recipes mentioned in the episode!
itunes:summary: Hop into that time machine, ‘cuz we’re blasting to the past with some retro food finds on this week’s episode of Chew the Right Thing!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
